<-@ Prompt @->
#@#
Create an HTML5 2D platformer game.
What it should include:
1. Main menu
2. First level
3. The goal is to collect all the coins and reach the portal at the end of the level.
4. The level will contain enemies and traps (spikes) that will hinder the character's progress.
#@#

